utility_evaluation.REASONING:
The format specifies six required items: property, financing, legal_services, moving_services, setup_services, and total_budget. The final property solution contains all six of these top-level items. Each one is fully specified with all relevant details: 
1) property — includes type, location, size, features, price, currency, and monthly fees; 
2) financing — includes purchase method, down payment (amount and percentage), interest rate, term, costs, fees, and approval details; 
3) legal_services — includes service name, cost, currency, and completion date; 
4) moving_services — includes service name, cost, currency, included features, and move date; 
5) setup_services — includes utilities setup and property survey with service names, costs, and currencies; 
6) total_budget — includes detailed cost breakdown and grand total. All expected items are present and fully detailed.

